'''珍·多萝西·茜宝'''（{{lang-en|Jean Dorothy Seberg}}，{{bd|1938年|11月13日|1979年|8月30日|catIdx=S}}）是一位美国女演员。她曾在[[好莱坞|好莱坞]]和欧洲的34部电影中担任主演，其中包括《聖女貞德》（出道）、《[[斷了氣|斷了氣]]》和《[[国际机场_(电影)|国际机场]]》等。

茜宝也是[[联邦调查局|FBI]]反谍项目的最著名的目标之一。她的受害有充分证据显示为对她在20世纪60年代支持[[黑豹党|黑豹党]]的报复。

珍·茜宝40岁时在巴黎服用巴比妥类药物过量而去世。她的死被裁定可能为自杀。

== 早年生活 ==
珍·茜宝出生于[[艾奥瓦州|艾奥瓦州]]马歇尔，母亲是一个代课老师，父亲是一个[[药剂师|药剂师]]。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F50E1EFA345C12728DDDA00894D1405B898BF1D3 | work=The New York Times | title=Jean Seberg Found Dead in Paris; Actress Was Missing for 10 Days; A Life of Personal Tragedy | date=1979-09-09 | accessdate=2010-05-06 | archive-date=2012-10-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121011074942/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F50E1EFA345C12728DDDA00894D1405B898BF1D3 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F40A13FE3F5512728DDDA90B94D9415B8084F1D3 | work=The New York Times | title=The Seberg Tragedy; Jean Seberg | date=1980-11-30 | accessdate=2010-05-06 | first=Mel | last=Gussow | archive-date=2012-10-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121011074954/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F40A13FE3F5512728DDDA90B94D9415B8084F1D3 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=lea>{{Cite web |url=http://www.genealogi.se/shf9731.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-07-27 |archive-date=2012-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311034506/http://www.genealogi.se/shf9731.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>她的家庭信仰[[信義宗|信義宗]]，具有瑞典，英格兰和德国血统。<ref name=lea/><ref>{{cite news | url=http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F60A17FD345A137A93C5A9178FD85F438585F9 | work=The New York Times | title=Evolution of a New Saint Joan; Jean Seberg, 18, unknown and barely tried, illustrates how a star is made, if not born | date=1957-04-07 | accessdate=2010-05-06 | first=Gilbert | last=Millstein | archive-date=2012-10-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121011074959/http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F60A17FD345A137A93C5A9178FD85F438585F9 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.alice-miller.com/articles_en.php?lang=en&nid=55&grp=11 |title=Alice Miller<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-07-27 |archive-date=2006-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061221011226/http://www.alice-miller.com/articles_en.php?lang=en&nid=55&grp=11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>珍有一个姐妹和两个兄弟。 

高中毕业后，茜宝来到[[艾奥瓦大学|艾奥瓦大学]]学习戏剧艺术，但后来由电影制作代替。<ref>"At the time I was due to audition for Preminger, I was enrolled to study dramatic art at the State University of Iowa, my eventual goal being stardom on Broadway, hopefully." Seberg in Films and Filming, p13, June 1974</ref>

==个人生活==
1958年10月5日茜宝与23岁的法国律师François Moreuil在马歇尔结婚。<ref>"Romain Gary a séduit mon épouse Jean Seberg". By François Moreuil. http://www.parismatch.com/People/Cinema/Romain-Gary-a-seduit-mon-epouse-Jean-Seberg-Par-Francois-Moreuil-148199 {{Wayback|url=http://www.parismatch.com/People/Cinema/Romain-Gary-a-seduit-mon-epouse-Jean-Seberg-Par-Francois-Moreuil-148199 |date=20140718055311 }} (retrieved 8 November 2013)</ref>1960年他们离婚。

1963年，茜宝嫁给了比她大24岁的法国小说家和外交官[[罗曼·加里|罗曼·加里]]，他们唯一的孩子Alexandre Diego Gary，1962年7月24日出生在巴塞罗那。在这段婚姻期间，茜宝居住在巴黎，[[希腊|希腊]]，[[法國南部|法國南部]]和[[馬略卡島|馬略卡島]]。<ref>"What makes Jean Seberg Run?", ''[[Tri-City_Herald|Tri-City Herald]]'', June 21, 1970, p. 8</ref>

茜宝的第二个孩子Nina Hart Gary（生于1970年8月23日 - 死于1970年8月25日，葬在艾奥瓦州马歇尔的河沿公墓），尽管加里承认孩子是自己的，但在怀孕期间，茜宝坦承，孩子是与一个叫Carlos Ornelas Navarro的学生外遇而来。<ref>(Spanish)[http://www.cineforever.com/2007/09/08/la-fragil-jean-seberg/ CineForEver: La Fragil Jean Seberg] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cineforever.com/2007/09/08/la-fragil-jean-seberg/ |date=20131109055918 }} (retrieved 10 August 2012)</ref>两人在Nina出生之前1个月离婚。<ref name="lakeland">{{cite news|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=LWVRAAAAIBAJ&sjid=J_sDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4580,1035973&dq=jean+seberg+suicide&hl=en|title=Jean Seberg not reason for novelist's suicide, note says|date=1980-12-04|work=Lakeland Ledger|page=12D|accessdate=2012-12-02|archive-date=2015-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123011735/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=LWVRAAAAIBAJ&sjid=J_sDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4580,1035973&dq=jean+seberg+suicide&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1972年，她与电影导演Dennis Berry开始第三段婚姻。

1979年她与丈夫分居，和阿尔及利亚人Ahmed Hasni开始伴侣关系。<ref>Richards, p.367</ref>他们前往西班牙，但很快茜宝就独自一人回到巴黎并躲开Hasni，她说曾受到很严重的[[家庭暴力|暴力虐待]]。<ref>Richards, p.369</ref>

== 去世 ==
[[File:Seberggrave.jpg|thumb]]

1979年8月下旬，茜宝失踪。她的伴侣Ahmed Hasni告诉警方，8月30日晚上他们看完一部电影，第二天早上，当他醒来的时候，茜宝已经离开。<ref name="pittsburg">{{cite news|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7Z5RAAAAIBAJ&sjid=6W0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6956,1534506&dq=jean+seberg+death&hl=en|title=Police Rule Out Violence In Death of Actress Seberg|date=1979-09-10|work=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette|page=21|accessdate=2012-12-02|archive-date=2015-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123011917/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7Z5RAAAAIBAJ&sjid=6W0DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6956,1534506&dq=jean+seberg+death&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>茜宝失踪后，Hasni告诉警方，他知道她想要自杀已经有一段时间了。他声称茜宝1979年7月曾在巴黎地铁列车前方跳下自杀未遂。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5wFlAAAAIBAJ&sjid=dIMNAAAAIBAJ&pg=897,4749074&dq=jean+seberg+suicide&hl=en|title=Forgive me, Seberg wrote in suicide note to her son|date=1979-09-10|work=Edmonton Journal|page=A2|accessdate=2012-12-02|archive-date=2015-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123011819/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5wFlAAAAIBAJ&sjid=dIMNAAAAIBAJ&pg=897,4749074&dq=jean+seberg+suicide&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

十天后，[[巴黎十六区|巴黎十六区]]茜宝公寓附近停放的她的[[雷诺|雷诺]]车的后座上发现了被毯子包裹着的她已经腐烂的尸体。警方发现了一瓶[[巴比妥类药物|巴比妥类药物]]，一个空矿泉水瓶和一张用法语写的给她儿子的纸条。她的死被警方裁定为自杀。<ref name=montreal>{{cite news|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=2FQ0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=abkFAAAAIBAJ&pg=5605,1267220&dq=jean+seberg+suicide+alcohol&hl=en|title=Charges filed in Seberg death|date=1979-06-23|work=The Montreal Gazette|page=41|accessdate=2012-12-02|archive-date=2015-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150904123952/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=2FQ0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=abkFAAAAIBAJ&pg=5605,1267220&dq=jean+seberg+suicide+alcohol&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

茜宝的第二任丈夫罗曼·加里在她去世后不久召开记者会，公开指责FBI对茜宝的打击使她的心理健康日益恶化。加里称1970年FBI编造了茜宝怀了黑豹党的孩子的谎言，媒体报道后茜宝就“成了精神病”。孩子由于早产在出生两天后就死亡。加里说，茜宝曾多次企图在孩子的逝世纪念日8月25日时自杀。<ref name="lakeland"/>

茜宝被埋葬在法国巴黎[[蒙帕纳斯公墓|蒙帕纳斯公墓]]。

